This directory contains scripts providing functions deemed useful across a broad 
spectrum of customers.

Although Apache Design Solutions, Inc., provides these scripts at no charge as an 
aid to our customers, there is no guarantee for support in resolving customer issues 
found running the scripts nor any guarantee for continuation of these scripts in 
future releases of RedHawk(TM).

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+ rh_setup.pl  quick setup utility for RedHawk
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+apl_std_setup.pl   Performs setup for APL and APLCAP characterization of std. cells in the design
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+avm_setup.pl   Generates configuration file for running AVM for all memories used in design
+ Read the file AVM_Primer.txt for a technical discussion of the AVM parameters.)
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+vds2avm.pl   Virage memory compiler datasheet to AVM conversion
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+checkDefLefLib.pl print cells that exist in DEF but miss in LEF or LIB
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+create_spi_ploc.pl  
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+decap2eco.pl  Apache decap ECO to Synopsys Scheme translation
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+gds_setup.pl   Generates configuration files and runs gds2def extraction for multiple cells
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+genHisto.pl  Creates histogram of instance based voltage drop or any other tabulated file
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+getLEF_pin.pl read through a list of LEF files and output the names and types of pins for a user provided list of cells
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+gridfix2scm.pl  Convert Apache grid ECOs into Synopsys Scheme format
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+mkmv.pl  Create an animated GIF of a RedHawk DvD movie cature
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+plotHsim.pl displays waveforms for chosen signals from HSIM/Nanosim simulation results in Apache signal viewer
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+ process_pad_current.pl  Splits combined pad current file into individual waveforms
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+saif2toggle.pl  Convert SAIF file into instance toggle file for Redhawk 
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+sim2iprof_setup.pl gen config file for running sim2iprof for conversion of memory .OUT files to Apache cell.current format 
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+send2apache.pl  Automatically transfers complete customer testcases to Apache
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+cpp2ploc.pl  Creates the connection from an external package model format to Redhawk ploc format
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+pwl2apl.pl   Generates APL current profiles from a variety of simple waveform formats
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+genscansp.pl  Generate the scan shift state propagation file for the Vectorless Scan flow
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+plotSwitchVoltageWaveformsForRampup.tcl  RedHawk TCL script to dump switch voltages from a list of instances
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+ lec2rh.pl  convert LEC Mapping file from Conformal/Verplex to RedHawk readable mapping file
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+ parser_power.pl   allow user to refine power results for a run based on user search criteria 
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+ analyse_RH_run.tcl   Documentation provided in Report_Generation_Scripts_ReadMe.pdf
+ 
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+
+ cpm2spice.pl  Automated creation of SPICE deck to generate Rdie/Cdie frequency spread for a CPM model
+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++


